Wiimotedev-daemon Changelog
===========================

Wiimotedev daemon 1.2
- NEW API, incompatible with 1.0 (change in service name)
- added new object /deviceEvents
- added new object /service
- added new interface org.wiimotedev.deviceEvents
- added new interface org.wiimotedev.service
- updated dbusReportUnregisterWiiremote() signal
- added dbusUnregistredWiiremoteList() method
- added dbusReloadSequenceList() method
- added dbusUnregistredWiiremoteList() method
- added dbusWiimoteGetStatus() method
- improved init.d scripts (now supports reload, restart)
- wiimotedev-daemon now works in group wiimotedev
- automated init.d scripts (creating groups)

Wiimotedev daemon 1.0-1
- dbusReportUnregisterWiiremote() signal
- unregistred devices are now automaticly disconnected
- added new reports for syslog 

Wiimotedev daemon 1.0 (stable)
- First public release
